    "source_section_latex": "\\[ u_{\\mathrm{mag}}(r,t)=\\frac{\\lvert B(r,t)\\rvert^{2}}{2\\mu_{0}}. \\] The total magnetic energy inside radius $R$ is \\[ U_{\\mathrm{mag}} = \\int_{0}^{R}\\int_{0}^{\\pi}\\int_{0}^{2\\pi} \\frac{\\lvert B(r,t)\\rvert^{2}}{2\\mu_{0}} r^{2}\\sin\\theta \\, dr\\, d\\theta\\, d\\phi. \\] Mechanical compression contributes the constraint energy \\[ U_{\\mathrm{constraint}}=U_{\\mathrm{mag}} + F_{\\mathrm{mech}} d, \\] where the force between opposite dipoles separated by distance $d$ is \\[ F_{\\mathrm{mech}} = \\frac{3\\mu_{0}}{2\\pi d^{4}} \\left( \\mu_{1}\\cdot\\mu_{2} - 2(\\mu_{1}\\cdot \\hat d)(\\mu_{2}\\cdot \\hat d) \\right). \\]\n\n\\[\nu_{B}=\\frac{B^{2}}{2\\mu_{0}}\n\\]\n\\[\nE_{B}=\\int_{\\Omega}u_{B}\\,dV\n\\]"
